<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Software Spectrum cut.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Software Spectrum cut.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Piper Jaffray Inc said it downgraded Software Spectrum Inc to market performer from buy.</p>
<p>-- said cut the third quarter earnings estimate to $0.16 a share from $0.58 a share. Cut the fourth quarter estimate to $0.42 a share from $0.71 and the fiscal year 1998 estimate to $2.90 a share from $3.62 a share.</p>
<p>-- Software Spectrum lost 6-3/8 to 27-1/8.</p>
<p>	  (( -- Wall Street desk 212-859-1730))</p>
